[
    {
        "text": "Hello, I'm Syndi Seid, an etiquette coach.",
        "startTime": 7200,
        "endTime": 10383,
        "slowStartTime": 10950,
        "slowEndTime": 15800
    },
    {
        "text": "Something people often ask me is how do you properly give an introduction in a business setting.",
        "startTime": 11233,
        "endTime": 17950,
        "slowStartTime": 17000,
        "slowEndTime": 27150
    },
    {
        "text": "So here is my two - step golden rule to proper introductions.",
        "startTime": 18700,
        "endTime": 23317,
        "slowStartTime": 28200,
        "slowEndTime": 35200
    },
    {
        "text": "First, always remember the first person's name out of your mouth...",
        "startTime": 23900,
        "endTime": 29260,
        "slowStartTime": 36000,
        "slowEndTime": 44115
    },
    {
        "text": "...should be the most important person's name.",
        "startTime": 29467,
        "endTime": 32317,
        "slowStartTime": 44350,
        "slowEndTime": 48700
    },
    {
        "text": "Thereafter, everyone else is introduced to that most important person.",
        "startTime": 32967,
        "endTime": 38650,
        "slowStartTime": 49600,
        "slowEndTime": 58200
    },
    {
        "text": "But actually, rank and status are the primary determinants to who takes precedence over whom.",
        "startTime": 39667,
        "endTime": 46950,
        "slowStartTime": 59650,
        "slowEndTime": 70650
    },
    {
        "text": "When introducing someone, never use the word \"meet\".",
        "startTime": 51233,
        "endTime": 54450,
        "slowStartTime": 77000,
        "slowEndTime": 81900
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, Jane Doe is the CEO of a company and John Smith is a new staff person.",
        "startTime": 54867,
        "endTime": 61417,
        "slowStartTime": 82450,
        "slowEndTime": 92350
    },
    {
        "text": "You would never want to say, \"Jane Doe, I would like you to meet John Smith.\"",
        "startTime": 62033,
        "endTime": 67583,
        "slowStartTime": 93200,
        "slowEndTime": 101600
    },
    {
        "text": "...because it actually throws the emphasis...",
        "startTime": 68133,
        "endTime": 71108,
        "slowStartTime": 102350,
        "slowEndTime": 106887
    },
    {
        "text": "...off the most important person on to that second person, John Smith.",
        "startTime": 71241,
        "endTime": 76383,
        "slowStartTime": 107012,
        "slowEndTime": 114800
    },
    {
        "text": "Rather, if you want an informal introduction, how about using the word, \"This is.\"",
        "startTime": 77267,
        "endTime": 83350,
        "slowStartTime": 116050,
        "slowEndTime": 125250
    },
    {
        "text": "Example, \"Jane Doe, this is John Smith.\"",
        "startTime": 83817,
        "endTime": 88450,
        "slowStartTime": 125875,
        "slowEndTime": 132900
    },
    {
        "text": "When using the more traditional word \"introduce,\" be careful not to get too wordy.",
        "startTime": 92633,
        "endTime": 98017,
        "slowStartTime": 139100,
        "slowEndTime": 147250
    },
    {
        "text": "For instance, which of these three sentences is correct?",
        "startTime": 98567,
        "endTime": 102517,
        "slowStartTime": 148000,
        "slowEndTime": 154000
    },
    {
        "text": "Is it a: Jane Doe, may I introduce John Smith.",
        "startTime": 103067,
        "endTime": 108783,
        "slowStartTime": 154750,
        "slowEndTime": 163400
    },
    {
        "text": "b: Ms. Doe, may I introduce to you Mr. Smith.",
        "startTime": 109667,
        "endTime": 114917,
        "slowStartTime": 164650,
        "slowEndTime": 172600
    },
    {
        "text": "Or c: Jane Doe, may I introduce you to John Smith.",
        "startTime": 115733,
        "endTime": 121850,
        "slowStartTime": 173750,
        "slowEndTime": 183000
    },
    {
        "text": "If you chose a or b, you would be correct.",
        "startTime": 122533,
        "endTime": 125717,
        "slowStartTime": 183950,
        "slowEndTime": 188800
    },
    {
        "text": "However, a is the best answer because it uses the fewest words.",
        "startTime": 126233,
        "endTime": 131183,
        "slowStartTime": 189500,
        "slowEndTime": 197000
    },
    {
        "text": "So here are a few other tips to keep in mind when introducing someone.",
        "startTime": 134367,
        "endTime": 138483,
        "slowStartTime": 201700,
        "slowEndTime": 207950
    },
    {
        "text": "Always keep the honorifics even.",
        "startTime": 139433,
        "endTime": 141783,
        "slowStartTime": 209300,
        "slowEndTime": 212900
    },
    {
        "text": "If you use Ms. Doe, you must use Mr. Smith.",
        "startTime": 142367,
        "endTime": 146717,
        "slowStartTime": 213700,
        "slowEndTime": 220300
    },
    {
        "text": "However, you can use first names such as Jane or John,...",
        "startTime": 147433,
        "endTime": 151917,
        "slowStartTime": 221300,
        "slowEndTime": 228100
    },
    {
        "text": "...but in this case you must include their last name as well.",
        "startTime": 152500,
        "endTime": 156450,
        "slowStartTime": 228900,
        "slowEndTime": 234900
    },
    {
        "text": "And lastly, do share some information about each person you're introducing...",
        "startTime": 158017,
        "endTime": 162883,
        "slowStartTime": 237175,
        "slowEndTime": 244550
    },
    {
        "text": "...so that they can springboard their conversation and you can exit to meet some other people.",
        "startTime": 163367,
        "endTime": 168783,
        "slowStartTime": 245200,
        "slowEndTime": 253400
    },
    {
        "text": "So there you have it, some quick tips on proper introductions.",
        "startTime": 170067,
        "endTime": 173983,
        "slowStartTime": 255250,
        "slowEndTime": 261200
    },
    {
        "text": "Happy practicing.",
        "startTime": 174700,
        "endTime": 175783,
        "slowStartTime": 262200,
        "slowEndTime": 263899
    }
]